OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry and warm
OL,6,Fthis evening for many, but with cloud
OL,7,Fbuilding through the evening. Low
OL,8,Fcloud likely spreading inland
OL,9,Fovernight and accompaned by a
OL,10,Fstrengthening easterly breeze.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FAny low cloud soon clearing
OL,13,Fto leave another dry day with sunny
OL,14,Fspells. Feeling noticeably cooler in
OL,15,Fthe brisk easterly breeze however,
OL,16,Fthough still rather warm in the far
OL,17,Fwest.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
