OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FVariable cloud, warm or very warm on
OL,7,FThursday and Friday with clear or
OL,8,Fsunny periods, but also a risk of
OL,9,Fshowers or thunderstorms. Warm,
OL,10,Fpotentially very warm on Saturday
OL,11,Fstill.
